HEADWORD: Neocene
<hw>Ne"o*cene</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Neo-</ets> +
Gr. <grk>ne`os</grk> new.]</ety> <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>More recent
